Name: UCSB
Description: A great university located along the California coast!

Name: Korean Bell of Friendship
Description: Donated by the Republic of Korea and located on top of a hill, it is a monument that offers a great view of the beach below the hill.

Name: The Sunken City
Description: Hangout spot beside a cliff that used to be a building, but collapsed due to a natural landslide.

Name: Cabrillo Beach Tide Pools
Description: Nearby Sunken City in San Pedro, the tide pools show a variety of marine life, especially enjoyable and prevalent during low tides.

Name: Mitsuwa Marketplace
Description: An amazing market that offers a wide variety of asian products and has a food court with tasty Japanese dishes.

Name: Santa Catalina Island
Description: An island with bisons, great diving spots, and amazing hike trails. Great place to visit with its multitude of attractions and scenic views at night.
